 @notice Demonstrates a rotating savings contract with customizable parameters:
         - Number of members
         - Frequency of contributions (in weeks)
         - Contribution amount (in Ether, supporting decimals)
         - Distribution interval (in weeks)
         - List of member addresses
 IMPORTANT: This is a simplified example and is NOT production-ready.
